Package: zurichdown
Title: An R Markdown thesis template customized for the University of Zurich
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Din", "Grobu", email = "zurichdown.promoter754@passmail.net", role = c("cre", "aut"))
    )
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    University of Zurich, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: dingrobu 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    here,
    R.utils
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - https://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
